name: Solitaire (Felix Jeske)
overview: Solit aka Solitaire is a freely-distributable, shareware non-Klondike solitaire card game for the Amiga by Felix R. Jeske, it runs under Workbench 2.x. This is version 1.13 which contains some enhancements to version 1.06 found on FF882. There were two versions, the demo and a full version with extra features like undo and so forth.
